    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098420/extras/fefdea4a2a9c497a8f07ac8b7e2aa7d7.webp?t=1768668328\" width=616 height=40 /></span><br>Step into the shoes of Alex Carter, a member of The Abducted, a UFO hunting group. Alex follows an anonymous tip to a location for nighttime sightings, unaware that he will be stumbling into a highly classified military facility. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098420/extras/3d854c75d906d9bec1476843773c9a96.webp?t=1768668328\" width=616 height=40 /></span><br>Exploration: Navigate the dark, foreboding halls with minimal lighting. This walking simulator immerses you in the eerie environment <strong>without</strong> the aid of a flashlight.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098420/extras/c646dddfc8636197d55ac879af32efdf.webp?t=1768668328\" width=616 height=40 /></span><br>Uncover the secrets of the classified facility through a narrative woven into audio logs and gameplay elements.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098420/extras/52e5e1e0d5cd1959e312901419d4751b.webp?t=1768668328\" width=616 height=40 /></span><br>Progress by interacting with objects like key cards, audio tapes, and documents to uncover the story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098420/extras/41e4559abf77d4cda2cd371d5eecb74f.webp?t=1768668328\" width=616 height=40 /></span><br>Immerse yourself in the game’s rich soundscape, meticulously designed to pull you deep into the atmosphere of a highly classified military base. The audio experience was thoughtfully crafted by three talented Musicians Institute graduates.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098420/extras/133d5d9cd536669ec2b09080e4aee22d.webp?t=1768668328\" width=616 height=40 /></span><br>We’re excited to announce that Nurbs Studios has teamed up with Default Gaming for an exclusive pre-release live stream of Installation 19! Join Default as he delves into the eerie world of the game before its official release. Stay tuned for more details coming soon!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098420/extras/cbdf1490f08bf9660dee555e5ec28c1c.poster.avif?t=1768668328\" width=572 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098420/extras/cbdf1490f08bf9660dee555e5ec28c1c.webm?t=1768668328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098420/extras/cbdf1490f08bf9660dee555e5ec28c1c.mp4?t=1768668328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>",
